    <item>
      <title>Spotify 扭亏为盈，付费用户数量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/spotify-boosts-paid-subscribers-in-first-quarter-beating-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Spotify Technology SA 的股价创下近两年来的最大涨幅，此前这家音频流媒体巨头报告称，由于该公司增加了订户并增加了新功能，该公司在第一季度实现了盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/spotify-boosts-paid-subscribers-in-first-quarter-beating-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 10:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因乐观盈利创下一月以来最佳单日表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/solid-earnings-from-novartis-sap-drive-european-stocks-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市创下自 1 月份以来最好的一天，诺华公司 (Novartis AG) 和 SAP SE 的强劲盈利报告掩盖了对利率的担忧。欧洲银行股飙升至2015年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/solid-earnings-from-novartis-sap-drive-european-stocks-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:25:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Telegram 允许使用 Tether 稳定币支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/telegram-messaging-service-to-allow-tether-stablecoin-payments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tether 是世界上最常用的稳定币发行商，它已与 TON 基金会合作，允许客户使用流行的 Telegram 加密即时消息服务发送加密支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/telegram-messaging-service-to-allow-tether-stablecoin-payments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 13:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
